metadata.name: Good vs Evil isn't always what it seems!
metadata.description:
This is my concept of good vs evil.
I created this from a thumbnail sketch I did one day at work. I then had to create each element separately and composite them together into the final illustration in Photoshop. 
 This piece was 1st displayed in "Ai Art Chill Polygon showcase" June 2022. 
tools used: Disco Diffusion, PS, Pen & Paper, imagination!
